            "chapterTitle": "Prohibition of facing the Graves during Salat (Prayer)",
            "urn": 1625580,
            "body": "<p>Abu Marthad Kannaz bin Husain (May Allah be pleased with him) said: I heard the Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) saying: \"Do not offer Salat (prayer) facing the graves and do not sit on them.\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
